执行以下代码会输出什么？
```java
try {
  return 1;
} catch (Exception e) {
  return 2;
} finally {
  return 3;
}
```

以下代码输出什么？
```java
Integer a = 127;
Integer b = 127;
Integer c = 128;
Integer d = 128;
System.out.println(a == b);
System.out.println(c == d);
```

以下代码输出什么？
```java
class A { String f() { return "A"; } }
class B extends A { String f() { return "B"; } }
public class Main {
  public static void main(String[] args) {
    A obj = new B();
    System.out.println(obj.f());
  }
}
```
